Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_enable..._compatibility(25.10)    timing_enable..._compatibility(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_path_delay_to_unconstrained_endpoints_compatibility

Syntax
       timing_enable_path_delay_to_unconstrained_endpoints_compatibility

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When set to true, the software does not constrain paths with path delay
       - if the path ends at an unconnected input pin of a combination cell.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

